{"tid":1407281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公務員罷工之不合作行動升級：放生鄉黑CY鄭若驊僭建嘅屋宇署！","createTime":"2019-08-04T15:06:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T05:35:59.000Z","uid":238693,"like":69,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"61ca7b30c41d5ad918c6e1609093719a3f045b66","tid":1407281,"uid":238693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:06:30.000Z","msg":"之前大家去稅務大樓幫公務員提早收工，發夢聽日終於有政府部門罷到有<span style=\"font-size: large;\">升級不合作行動</span>可以做，重要係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有意放生丁屋僭建，梁振英同鄭若驊僭建咩事都冇嘅 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屋宇署</span></span></span>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有朋友發夢夢見<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日屋宇署地下詢問及收發部會幾乎真空</span></span>，只是臨時搵咗幾個生手同事坐鎮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。如果有朋友對屋宇事宜有查詢及疑問，例如應該填咩表格，文盲唔識填表，懷疑有僭建物/危險建築物想舉報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">或是對署長張天祥有咩意見</span></span>，可要求相關組別職員直接回應。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n突然有大量公眾查詢，一定對部門產生壓力，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">尤其是啲中高層公務員咁鍾意返工，就俾多啲嘢佢哋做</span></span>，個署長張天祥又出名怕事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，絕對唔敢直接回應，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">分分鐘加多兩錢肉緊睇下元朗村屋啲僭建添</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">聽日歡迎大家到訪油麻地海庭道11號西九龍政府合署北座屋宇署總部</span></span>，尤其是嫌罷工集會悶嘅和理非手足～<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">八月五日三罷，一齊勇武！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},